			<h1 itemprop="name headline  ">Lebedev buys Independent newspapers</h1>
		
					<div itemprop="description" id="stand-first" class="stand-first-alone" data-component="Article:standfirst_cta">Russian billionaire finalises months of negotiations by buying papers for £1 from Independent News &amp; Media<br/><br/><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20140819192825/http://image.guardian.co.uk/sys-files/Media/documents/2010/03/25/INM_Statement_on_London_Independent_Disposal_25_Mar_10-2.pdf">Read the Independent News &amp; Media statement in full (pdf)</a><br/><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20140819192825/http://image.guardian.co.uk/sys-files/Media/documents/2010/03/25/IPLstatement.pdf">Read Independent Print Limited's statement in full (pdf)</a><br/><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20140819192825/http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/gallery/2010/mar/04/independent-proprietors-shareholders?picture=360032114">In pictures: Independent proprietors and shareholders</a><br/><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20140819192825/http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/theindependent+alexander-lebedev">The Independent and Lebedev: full coverage</a></div>
		
		
